KWallet 6.28.0 Secret Service compatibility fixes

Keep the released KWallet client ABI and D-Bus interface unchanged. These fixes
only correct ownership and argument-order bugs in the compatibility daemon used
between unmodified KF6 Wallet clients and a standards-compliant Secret Service.

